  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Extremely valuable interstellar trading mineral, typically <span class=\"name name-commodity\">mined from asteroids</span>. Occasionally found in underground planetary deposits.<br><br>Universally prized for its hardiness and versatility.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "极其珍贵的星际交易矿物，通常<span class=\"name name-commodity\">采掘自小行星</span>。有时可在地下行星沉积物中发现。<br><br>因其抗性和通用性而广受赞誉。",
    "TencentChinese": "极其珍贵的星际交易矿物，通常<span class=\"name name-commodity\">采掘自小行星</span>。有时可在地下行星沉积物中发现。<br><br>因其抗性和通用性而广受赞誉。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "極度珍貴的星際交易礦物，通常<span class=\"name name-commodity\">從小行星開採而來</span>。有時能在星球地底資源產地找到。<br><br>硬度高而用途廣，因而廣受珍視。"
  },
